  <official_title>A Phase 2 Trial of Standard of Care Treatment Versus Mesenchymal Stromal Cell Therapy Together With Standard of Care for the Treatment of de Novo Acute Graft Versus Host Disease Following Allogeneic Bone Marrow Transplantation</official_title>
