  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Grades 2-4 acute graft versus host disease after bone marrow transplantation up to day
             +180 after transplantation

          -  Age 18-55 years

               -  Must be receiving a calcineurin inhibitor

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Failure to sign informed consent

          -  Corticosteroid therapy for 72 hours or greater

          -  ECOG score equal to or greater than 3
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
